body_html: This looks like a duplicate of #5932. There's some new information, but not enough that I can easily reproduce or diagnose the problem. Unless there's good evidence of a bug, this kind of question is better asked on stackoverflow. You're more likely to get a helpful response if you can reduce it to an easily reproduced problem. Just guessing, I think maybe your model structure isn't what you think it is, so the wrong values are being propagated where labels are expected. Or alternatively, you're feeding the wrong format data.
